Third Part - Her setting.

items.name: Watanabe Saki (Shinsekai Yori)
items.description:
This is a lycors\locon you have to use the additional networks extension or the lycoris extension for this to work.

If you want to stay updated check out my Twitter

So time for another one. So I was really confused when i watched the anime the first time and the community is pretty split on if it is a masterpiece or a disaster. From memory I would say I liked it but I would have to rewatch it to give a recommendation.

I didn't train on pictures of the anime I chose to stick to the manga because I like her design more for obvious reasons.

In the manga she skips the child phase and goes straight from this to full adult. Which I prefer because I really hate how children are depicted in anime they don't really behave like real children they are more like small adults.

I used "Shinsekai" as activation token because "Saki" and and "Watanabe Saki" or just "Watanabe" where all already associated with a character. Saki might have worked but all the other combination were doomed because this model has one or two problems that make it a bit weird to use.

The problems are that there are only 3 colored images in the dataset. You don't get monochrom pictures though unless you tag for them. The real problem is that the model doesn't know the right colors for her hair and her eyes (funny enough it gets the clothes right most of the time).

I used brown hair and purple eyes for the preview pictures but you can also use purple hair or black hair and you can also change the eyecolor with ease I think. You can also change her outfit and if you go to strength 0.8 or below it shouldn't have any resemblance to her default outfit. Only this outfit is included i tried to get the outfit from the first chapters as well but it doesn't really work.

Thanks for reading and if you like the model you can leave a like, rate and comment that would be appreciated.

Have fun generating.

items.name: Makoto_Shinkai_style——新海诚风格大模型
items.description:
新海诚动画电影风格的大模型，以NovalAI全量模型作为底模，通过一百多张《你的名字/君の名は》和几张《天气之子/天気の子》的高清截图为训练素材训练而成，以风景和画风为主，只有少量人物素材，直接出图或是高清修复效果都还不错，基本风格已经学到了，具体细节可能有些瑕疵，但不影响整体效果。这是本人第一次使用dreambooth训练大模型，本来是打算把诚哥的灾难三部曲《你的名字/君の名は》、《天气之子/天気の子》和《铃芽之旅/すずめの戸締まり》全部截完再一起训练的，由于截图要边看视频边找合适的画面，所以速度比较慢，目前刚截完《你的名字/君の名は》，《天气之子/天気の子》才开始，所以主要素材还只有《你的名字/君の名は》。这个模型最初是用来练手的，dreambooth训练大模型要比训练lora模型对硬件要求高很多，我的移动端3080/16G显卡已经捉襟见肘了，最主要是显存不够，经过几次炸炉和微调参数后，发现这个模型训练得还不错就保存了下来，相对而言《你的名字/君の名は》的画风我更喜欢，色彩比较明亮，单独拉出来也没啥问题，之后等全部截完图后再训练一版全量的看看怎么样。

配合EasyNegative等负面提示词模型效果较好，可以高清修复和超分放大获得分辨率更高、效果更好的图，出风景比较好，人物形象可能稍微单一一点，人物要出近景图，远距离容易崩，与Lora结合暂时还没有尝试。
